      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Block drums or round objects. Tilt the mast FORWARD and side the fork tips along the
          floor to get under the load. </p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_udc_xyy_5gc">
                     <image href="media/image803.png" id="image_wdc_xyy_5gc" placement="inline"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Before lifting, tilt the mast BACK slightly until the load is cradled on the
          forks.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
